post_install() {
  cat <<EOF

Note that the browser Ghostery Dawn is still in Beta.

Launch command: /usr/bin/ghostery

To use the builtin ad-free search (Ghostery Glow), a subscription is needed.
If you want to try it out, you can get one for free by signing up for the beta:

  https://www.ghostery.com/products/ghostery-browser/

EOF
}
